{"tid":2440814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"now工程人員稱遭警暴索償  無視命令遲交文件 律政司被官狠批","createTime":"2021-03-10T08:18:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T08:20:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1c9236e612c8fe9a0df64d8465b405137ec287","tid":2440814,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/LRP4OGRCYNBR7KHMY5RXTQACKM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FLRP4OGRCYNBR7KHMY5RXTQACKM%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=b66ac39b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FLRP4OGRCYNBR7KHMY5RXTQACKM%2F&h=c701019c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/LRP4OGRCYNBR7KHMY5RXTQACKM/</a><br />\n<br />\nnow工程人員稱遭警暴索償 <br />\n無視命令遲交文件 律政司被官狠批<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】now新聞台工程人員李小龍2014年在佔旺區採訪時，突遭警員搶走鋁梯，隨後反被指襲警被捕。他稱多名警員拘捕時把他按地拳打腳踢，身體多處受傷，並有創傷後壓力症狀，前年入稟區域法院向警方索償。案件將於下月開審，代表警隊的律政司被揭無視法庭命令，遲交文件達一個月之久。法官不信律政司解釋稱看漏眼，直言不可寄望原告能「奇蹟地」快速審閱文件作回應，下令負責本案的政府律師甚或律政司高層，向法庭寫信交代。<br />\n<br />\n案件昨進行審前覆核，法官李樹旭指，律政司一方遲遲未呈交審訊文件冊編號索引，上周才完成，足足比法庭命令的限期遲一個月。法官質疑律政司是否將文件擱在一旁不理，反問怎能期望原告能「奇蹟地」（miraculously）對遲交文件作出回應，更揚言若律政司無視命令，法庭下達命令也變得無意義。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KL7VeN8-UJf23KpxucPi5BW9NDI=/802x438/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WYNYKOQQVBDVXFN6LRBBSF7YPQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKL7VeN8-UJf23KpxucPi5BW9NDI%3D%2F802x438%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWYNYKOQQVBDVXFN6LRBBSF7YPQ.jpg&h=8f6a5deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■2014年now新聞台工程人員李小龍採訪時稱遭警員搶走鋁梯兼拳打腳踢，案件將於4月8日開審。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警員記事冊字迹難辨<br />\n<br />\n律政司代表回應稱疏忽看漏眼（oversight），法官不滿解釋，稱看不到如此犯錯會是看漏眼所致，即使小型律師行也不會發生如此情況，何況是有層層監督的律政司。法官下令負責本案的律政司人員在三天內，以書面完滿解釋為何不遵從法庭命令，法庭之後再考慮有否進一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n至於預審內容，原告指警方提供的片段攝於流動工作台上，拍不到工作台下方原告被打情況。律政司不同意，稱片段拍到事發前原告的行為及與警方發生過甚麼事，與案有緊密關係。律政司指，原告在案發前某些動作構成拘捕理由，警方不是非法濫捕，但拘捕時原告嘗試抗拒警方制服，構成襲警。<br />\n<br />\n此外，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n法官閱讀後指譯文雖然不完美，但未至於令人不明白內容；又指譯文並不是昨天才出現，律政司早已閱讀，而處理核證譯本需時，拒絕律政司申請。<br />\n<br />\n案件按原定排期在4月8日開審，預計審6天。法官散庭前明言希望案件順利開審，「不要再有驚喜」。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：DCPI1635/19<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7toj0D2PFJ7a9C0hfn4Bm7CdC1A=/802x1069/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CPFXCM5JURHSRGKQHVSSKQNLH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7toj0D2PFJ7a9C0hfn4Bm7CdC1A%3D%2F802x1069%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCPFXCM5JURHSRGKQHVSSKQNLH4.jpg&h=6f9a94d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李小龍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/X1RiumxeeJWgJ9z_F89dx-WoWUE=/802x1122/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CBEWVFM7MJGTNJY3XSYGUZ224E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FX1RiumxeeJWgJ9z_F89dx-WoWUE%3D%2F802x1122%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCBEWVFM7MJGTNJY3XSYGUZ224E.jpg&h=28883bfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法官李樹旭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ftO2s9csXoFEdCl_3-kMgHqKaVc=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I3E2NQXZP5B6JPARRFJDXSGRGQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FftO2s9csXoFEdCl_3-kMgHqKaVc%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI3E2NQXZP5B6JPARRFJDXSGRGQ.jpg&h=5085663f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n律政司長鄭若驊"},{"pid":"7acad90be52f266292d7078d84b51c305ddbd176","tid":2440814,"uid":334957,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:19:36.000Z","msg":"屌你，兩個撞樣?"},{"pid":"0e81a1f51a8ed1756d9abadd2211fa819fe0f87a","tid":2440814,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:20:15.000Z","msg":"now新聞台工程人員李小龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> be water"}]}